an Naylor]]\n|''[[Army Times]]''\n|\n|<ref name=\"WHCA Names 2003 Award Winners\" />\n|-\n|Staff\n|''[[South Florida Sun-Sentinel]]''\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHCA Names 2003 Award Winners\" />\n|-\n|Michael Berens\n|''[[Chicago Tribune]]''\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHCA Names 2003 Award Winners\" />\n|-\n|rowspan=7|2004\n|Russell Corollo and Mei-ling Hopgood\n|''Dayton Daily News''\n|\n|<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|Christopher H. Schmitt and Edward T. Pound\n|''U.S. News & World Report''\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|Michael Hudson\n|[[Southern Exposure (magazine)|''Southern Exposure'' magazine]]\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|Warren P. Strobel and Jonathan S. Landy\n|[[Knight Ridder]]\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|Rod Nordland and Michael Hirsh\n|''Newsweek''\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|Sami Yousafzai, Ron Moreau, and Michael Hirsh\n|''Newsweek''\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|[[Fareed Zakaria]]\n|''Newsweek''\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2004 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2005\n|[[Mark Fainaru-Wada]] and [[Lance Williams and Mark Fainaru-Wada|Lance Williams]]\n|''[[The San Francisco Chronicle]]''\n|\n|<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2005 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|[[Donald Barlett]] and [[James B. Steele|James Steele]]\n|[[Time (magazine)|''Time'' magazine]]\n|\n|Honorable Mention<ref name=\"WHITE HOUSE CORRESPONDENTS\u2019 ASSOCIATION NAMES 2005 AWARD WINNERS\" />\n|-\n|rowspan